      • arguments

        public final List<Expression> arguments(Expression rowIndex)
        从接口复制的说明: WinAggResultContext
        Returns Linq4j form of arguments. The resulting value is equivalent to rowTranslator().translateList(rexArguments()). This is handy if you need just operate on argument.
        指定者:
        arguments 在接口中 WinAggResultContext
        参数:
        rowIndex - index of the requested row. The index must be in range of partition's startIndex and endIndex.
        返回:
        Linq4j form of arguments of the particular row

        参数:

      • index

        public Expression index()
        从接口复制的说明: WinAggFrameContext
        Returns the index of the current row in the partition. In other words, it is close to ~ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW. Note to use WinAggFrameContext.startIndex() when you need zero-based row position.
        指定者:
        index 在接口中 WinAggFrameContext
        返回:
        the index of the very first row in partition
